                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18160110-24-off131 t18160110-24-cd132"></join>, one bag of cotton, value 5s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18160110-24-victim246" type="victimName">
